# 📌 Project Overview

This project is a **Django-based E-Commerce web application** developed using **Python and the Django framework**.

The project follows a **modular Django architecture**, where different apps handle different functionalities of the website.

The application uses:

✔ **Class-Based Views (CBVs)** for page rendering and main logic  
✔ **Function-Based Views (FBVs)** for handling forms and redirects  

The goal of this project is to **learn and practice full-stack web development using Django**.

---

# ✨ Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| 🔐 **User Authentication** | Secure login and registration system for users |
| 🛍 **Product Browsing** | Users can explore products organized into categories |
| 🛒 **Shopping Cart** | Add, remove, and manage products in the cart |
| 📩 **Contact System** | Users can send messages and feedback through the contact form |
| 📄 **Information Pages** | Includes pages like Terms & Conditions |
| 🎨 **Responsive Design** | Clean and responsive interface for better usability |
| ⚙ **Modular Django Apps** | Structured with multiple apps for scalability |

---

# 🛠 Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|-----------|--------|
| 🐍 Python | Backend programming language |
| 🌐 Django | Web framework |
| 🧱 HTML | Page structure |
| 🎨 CSS / Bootstrap | Styling and responsive layout |
| ⚡ JavaScript | Frontend interaction |
| 🔄 AJAX | Dynamic content updates |
| 🗄 SQLite | Database management |

