### 💻 Technical Learning (Code Perspective)

🧱 **Django Models**  
Learned how to design database structures and manage application data using Django ORM.

🌐 **Views (CBV & FBV)**  
Understood how Django processes user requests and returns responses using both Class-Based and Function-Based views.

🧩 **Templates**  
Built dynamic pages by combining Django Template Language with HTML structure.

🔗 **URL Routing**  
Learned how URLs connect users to the correct application logic.

🔐 **Authentication System**  
Implemented login and signup functionality for user access control.

🛒 **Cart Functionality**  
Developed the logic for adding, removing, and managing items in a shopping cart.

📂 **Static & Media Handling**  
Managed static assets such as CSS, JavaScript, and images within the Django project.

⚡ **AJAX Integration**  
Improved user experience by updating page content dynamically without full page reloads.

